sentence: what is the minimum connection time for houston intercontinental
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  v0.minimum_connect_time, '"'||v0.airport_code||'"' FROM airport v0 
WHERE (v0.airport_code = 'IAH');
sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT AIRPORT.MINIMUM_CONNECT_TIME FROM AIRPORT WHERE AIRPORT.AIRPORT_CODE = ' IAH ' ) ;
